p&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong>HTML <code>&lt;html&gt;</code> 요소</strong>는 HTML 문서의 루트(최상단 요소)를 나타내며, \"루트 요소\"라고도 부릅니다. 모든 다른 요소는 <code>&lt;html&gt;</code> 요소의 후손이어야 합니다.</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\">콘텐츠 카테고리</a></th>\n   <td>없음.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">가능한 콘텐츠</th>\n   <td>하나의 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/head\"><code>&lt;head&gt;</code></a> 요소와 그 뒤를 따르는 하나의 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/body\"><code>&lt;body&gt;</code></a> 요소.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">태그 생략</th>\n   <td><code>&lt;html&gt;</code> 요소 내부의 첫 번째 것이 주석이 아니라면 시작 태그를 생략할 수 있습니다.<br>\n    <code>&lt;html&gt;</code> 요소 바로 뒤에 주석이 따라오지 않는다면 종료 태그를 생략할 수 있습니다.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">가능한 부모 요소</th>\n   <td>없음. <code>&lt;html&gt;</code>이 문서의 루트 요소입니다.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">암시적 ARIA 역할</th>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html-aria/#dfn-no-corresponding-role\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">대응하는 역할 없음</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">가능한 ARIA 역할</th>\n   <td>없음</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">DOM 역할</th>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLHtmlElement\"><code>HTMLHtmlElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"특성","title":"특성","isH3":false,"content":"<p><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">이 요소는 </span><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes\">전역 특성</a><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">을 포함합니다.</span></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"manifest\"><a id=\"attr-manifest\" href=\"#attr-manifest\"><b><code>manifest</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>지역적으로 캐시되어야하는 리소스를 가리키는 매니페스트 리소스의 URI를 나타냅니다. 자세한 내용은 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Using_the_application_cache\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">애플리케이션 캐시 사용하기</a>를 보세요.</dd>\n <dt id=\"version\"><a id=\"attr-version\" href=\"#attr-version\"><b><code>version</code></b></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>현재 문서를 제어하는 HTML 문서 타입 정의의 버전을 나타냅니다. 하지만 이미 문서 타입 선언이 버전을 나타내고 있기 떄문에 이 속성은 필요하지 않습니다.</dd>\n <dt id=\"xmlns\"><a id=\"attr-xmlns\" href=\"#attr-xmlns\"><b><code>xmlns</code></b></a></dt>\n <dd>문서의 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/XML\">XML <small>(en-US)</small></a> <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\">네임스페이스</a>를 지정합니다. 기본값은 <code>\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"</code>입니다. XML <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Parser\">구문 분석기 <small>(en-US)</small></a>로 분석한 문서에는 필수이고, <code>text/html</code> 문서에서는 선택사항입니다.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"예제","title":"예제","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">DOCTYPE</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">lang</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>ko<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>...<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>...<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"접근성 고려사항","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>html</code> 요소의 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-lang\"><code>lang</code></a> 특성에 <a href=\"https://www.ietf.org/rfc/bcp/bcp47.txt\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">유효한 IETF 언어 식별 태그</a>를 지정하면 스크린 리더가 음성 표현에 사용할 언어를 선택할 때 도움이 됩니다. 언어 식별 태그는 페이지의 주 언어를 가리켜야 합니다. 아무런 값도 지정하지 않을 시 보통 운영체제의 언어 설정을 따라가므로, 잘못된 발음을 사용할 수 있습니다.</p>\n\n<p>또한 <code>&lt;html&gt;</code> 요소에 유효한 <code>lang</code> 선언이 존재해야 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a>과 같은 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/head\"><code>&lt;head&gt;</code></a> 내부의 중요한 메타데이터를 정확한 발음으로 표현할 수 있습니다.</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/Understanding_WCAG/Understandable#Guideline_3.1_%E2%80%94_Readable_Make_text_content_readable_and_understandable\">MDN Understanding WCAG, Guideline 3.1 explanations</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2016/NOTE-UNDERSTANDING-WCAG20-20161007/meaning-doc-lang-id.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Understanding Success Criterion 3.1.1 | W3C Understanding WCAG 2.0</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"명세","id":"specifications_2","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/semantics.html#the-html-element","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"html.elements.html"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"브라우저 호환성","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.html","dataURL":"/ko/docs/Web/HTML/Element/html/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"같이_보기","title":"같이 보기","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>MathML 최상위 요소 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;math&gt; (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li>SVG 최상위 요소 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"특성","id":"특성"},{"text":"예제","id":"예제"},{"text":"접근성 고려사항","id":"specifications"},{"text":"명세","id":"specifications_2"},{"text":"브라우저 호환성","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"같이 보기","id":"같이_보기"}],"summary":"HTML <html> 요소는 HTML 문서의 루트(최상단 요소)를 나타내며, \"루트 요소\"라고도 부릅니다. 모든 다른 요소는 <html> 요소의 후손이어야 합니다.","popularity":0.0002,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<html>: The HTML Document / Root element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<html>","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<html> : l'élément de racine du document HTML","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<html>: HTML 文書 / ルート要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<html>","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (d